14
00:01:06,875 --> 00:01:08,114
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami mendapat telepon...</font>

15
00:01:09,515 --> 00:01:10,545
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk menjemputnya.</font>

16
00:01:13,355 --> 00:01:14,384
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat itu...</font>

17
00:01:16,325 --> 00:01:17,925
<font color=#FFFF00>...pertarungan sesungguhnya dimulai.</font>

18
00:01:20,254 --> 00:01:21,724
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku pikir ingatan Ayahku...</i></font>

19
00:01:22,024 --> 00:01:23,894
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...berhenti saat berada
di markas pemberontak.</i></font>

20
00:01:26,965 --> 00:01:29,265
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Mungkin dia berpikir Seoul
tempat yang luas.</i></font>

21
00:01:30,935 --> 00:01:32,134
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia tidak pernah berhenti...</i></font>

22
00:01:33,075 --> 00:01:34,405
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...melarikan diri.</i></font>

23
00:01:40,845 --> 00:01:41,845
