<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah!</font>

25
00:01:51,254 --> 00:01:52,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus kabur.</font>

26
00:02:13,675 --> 00:02:16,644
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku belajar untuk ujianku,
bekerja shift malam,</i></font>

27
00:02:17,515 --> 00:02:19,054
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan bermain petak umpet...</i></font>

28
00:02:20,015 --> 00:02:22,355
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dengan Ayahku setiap hari.</i></font>

29
00:02:23,925 --> 00:02:25,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak apa-apa, Ayah.</font>

30
00:02:27,925 --> 00:02:29,325
