tidak membuat kesalahan seperti ini.</font>

40
00:02:58,094 --> 00:02:59,524
<font color=#FFFF00>Ingat.</font>

41
00:02:59,524 --> 00:03:01,964
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasien meninggal karena kau.</font>

42
00:03:02,225 --> 00:03:03,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bukan Dokter.</font>

43
00:03:19,045 --> 00:03:20,415
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat itulah...</font>

44
00:03:21,584 --> 00:03:23,015
<font color=#FFFF00>...tangan kiriku jadi tidak berguna.</font>

45
00:03:31,755 --> 00:03:34,195
<font color=#FFFF00>Setiap Ayahku sadar,
dia meminta...</font>

46
00:03:35,195 --> 00:03:36,825
<font color=#FFFF00>...padaku beberapa morfin.</font>

47
00:03:38,635 --> 00:03:39,894
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi dia bisa mati.</font>

48
00:03:43,105 --> 00:03:44,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah itu lucu?</font>

49
00:03:46,235 --> 00:03:48,175
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang Ayah dokter ingin...</font>

50
00:03:48,175 --> 00:03:50,575
<font color=#FFFF00>...anak Dokternya
membunuh dia.</font>

51
00:03:54,415 --> 00:03:56,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah alasan...</font>

52
00:03:57,184 --> 00:03:59,255
