<font color=#FFFF00>Anda tahu dimana sekarang?</font>

91
00:08:17,145 --> 00:08:18,215
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa...</font>

92
00:08:18,215 --> 00:08:20,244
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Kwak yang membawamu.</font>

93
00:08:24,184 --> 00:08:26,384
