94
00:08:33,125 --> 00:08:34,824
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

95
00:08:36,194 --> 00:08:38,635
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menderita sakit perut
yang mengerikan.</font>

96
00:08:39,934 --> 00:08:41,334
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah baikan sekarang.</font>

97
00:08:42,535 --> 00:08:44,734
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya aku bisa...</font>

98
00:08:44,734 --> 00:08:47,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda mau keluar lagi?</font>

99
00:08:48,474 --> 00:08:49,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

100
00:08:50,545 --> 00:08:52,714
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini hanya solusi sementara.</font>

101
00:08:53,474 --> 00:08:55,415
<font color=#FFFF00>Tanpa perawatan apapun,</font>

102
00:08:56,684 --> 00:08:59,155
<font color=#FFFF00>...semua akan bertambah buruk.</font>

103
00:08:59,155 --> 00:09:00,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi.../ Bulan November nanti,</font>

104
00:09:02,084 --> 00:09:04,054
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku akan menerbitkan
buku puisi.</font>

105
00:09:05,495 --> 00:09:08,064
<font color=#FFFF00>Isinya masih sedikit,
dan aku harus...</font>

106
00:09:08,064 --> 00:09:09,625
<font color=#FFFF00>...lanjutkan menulis.</font>

107
00:09:11,295 --> 00:09:12,464
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasien.</font>

108
00:09:13,064 --> 00:09:16,104
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah menulis
lebih dari 10 tahun.</font>

109
