<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa
tiba-tiba berhenti.</font>

110
00:09:18,405 --> 00:09:20,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak boleh begini
pada pembacaku.</font>

111
00:09:21,175 --> 00:09:23,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang paling penting,</font>

112
00:09:24,005 --> 00:09:27,275
<font color=#FFFF00>...piknik musim gugur
bersama anak-anak.</font>

113
00:09:28,484 --> 00:09:29,615
<font color=#FFFF00>Enam bulan.</font>

114
00:09:30,915 --> 00:09:33,115
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda mungkin suka
mengajar dan menulis,</font>

115
00:09:33,854 --> 00:09:37,495
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi Anda hanya bisa melakukannya
selama enam bulan lagi.</font>

116
00:09:38,995 --> 00:09:41,265
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemungkinan terburuk.../
Tiga bulan.</font>

117
00:09:44,934 --> 00:09:46,734
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku punya waktu tiga bulan.</font>

118
00:09:48,064 --> 00:09:50,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu waktu yang lama.</font>

119
00:09:51,005 --> 00:09:53,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku mati ketika operasi,</font>

120
00:09:53,405 --> 00:09:56,204
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku bahkan tidak bisa
memimpikan itu lagi.</font>

121
00:10:17,934 --> 00:10:19,365
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ingin keluar.</font>

122
00:10:20,165 --> 00:10:21,934
<font color=#FFFF00>Secepatnya.</font>

123
00:10:22,765 --> 00:10:24,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia harus naik kapal pertama...</font>

124
00:10:25,905 --> 00:10:27,844
<font color=#FFFF00>...supaya sampai
kekelas tepat waktu.</font>

125
00:10:30,275 --> 00:10:31,574
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau masih...</font>

126
00:10:33,015 --> 00:10:35,045
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak mau membujuknya?</font>

127
00:10:36,984 --> 00:10:40,054
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bukannya mengatakan
harga dirinya tidak penting.</font>

128
00:10:40,655 --> 00:10:41,724
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

129
00:10:44,354 --> 00:10:47,054
<font color=#FFFF00>...apa itu lebih penting dari hidupnya?</font>

130
00:10:54,304 --> 00:10:58,104
<font color=#FFFF00>Langit dan laut sama-sama biru,</font>

131
00:10:58,505 --> 00:10:59,834
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi tidak seperti kemarin.</font>

132
00:11:01,604 --> 00:11:03,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sangat berbeda.</font>

133
00:11:05,175 --> 00:11:06,574
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku Dokternya,</font>

134
00:11:07,785 --> 00:11:09,515
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku punya hak,</font>

135
00:11:10,084 --> 00:11:12,084
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku seharusnya tidak mengikutimu.</font>

136
00:11:13,915 --> 00:11:16,125
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku tidak bisa membujukmu,
aku harus menculikmu...</font>

137
00:11:16,525 --> 00:11:18,324
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan membawamu
ke ruang operasi.</font>

138
00:11:19,995 --> 00:11:21,125
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun.</font>

139
00:11:21,564 --> 00:11:23,895
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan pertarungan
tapi pertolongan dokter.</font>

140
00:11:24,295 --> 00:11:25,895
<font color=#FFFF00>Kematian adalah kegagalan.</font>

141
00:11:26,694 --> 00:11:27,934
<font color=#FFFF00>Apapun yang orang katakan,</font>

142
00:11:28,734 --> 00:11:30,464
<font color=#FFFF00>...kematian adalah
sebuah kegagalan.</font>

143
00:11:30,665 --> 00:11:34,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya seorang
Dokter sepertiku,</font>

144
00:11:35,545 --> 00:11:37,944
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak akan menerima
kegagalan dengan mudah.</font>

145
00:11:38,515 --> 00:11:41,115
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku seharusnya tidak menyerah.
Aku harus berjuang.</font>

146
00:11:42,944 --> 00:11:45,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa alasanmu mengatakan kematian
sebagai kegagalan?</font>

147
00:11:46,255 --> 00:11:49,724
<font color=#FFFF00>Kematian pasti datang pada semua orang.</font>

148
00:11:49,824 --> 00:11:51,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa itu bisa jadi kegagalan?</font>

149
00:11:53,025 --> 00:11:55,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Kematian adalah akhir,
bukan kegagalan.</font>

150
00:11:56,265 --> 00:11:59,165
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah akhir yang aku pilih.</font>

151
00:12:00,234 --> 00:12:04,474
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa bilang
tidak takut,</font>

152
00:12:05,135 --> 00:12:06,505
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku baik-baik saja.</font>

153
00:12:09,545 --> 00:12:10,844
<font color=#FFFF00>Istriku...</font>

154
00:12:11,275 --> 00:12:14,314
<font color=#FFFF00>...telah menunggu selama 10 tahun.</font>

155
00:12:15,984 --> 00:12:19,554
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pemalu dan sulit mendapat teman.</font>

156
00:12:19,554 --> 00:12:21,724
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti sangat kesepian.</font>

157
00:12:22,925 --> 00:12:24,094
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin...</font>

158
00:12:26,954 --> 00:12:28,765
<font color=#FFFF00>...pergi dan menemuinya.</font>

159
00:12:33,464 --> 00:12:34,865
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

160
00:12:35,905 --> 00:12:37,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan terima kasih.</font>

161
00:12:39,074 --> 00:12:40,474
<font color=#FFFF00>Matamu.</font>

162
00:12:41,204 --> 00:12:44,214
<font color=#FFFF00>Matamu selalu menatapku,
khawatir padaku,</font>

163
00:12:44,645 --> 00:12:47,275
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan terkadang, lebih sakit dari aku.</font>

164
00:12:47,484 --> 00:12:50,984
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena mata itu,
aku jadi tidak sakit.</font>

165
00:12:57,594 --> 00:12:59,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu,</font>

166
00:13:01,165 --> 00:13:02,895
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pikir...</font>

167
00:13:04,265 --> 00:13:05,995
<font color=#FFFF00>...matamu,</font>

168
00:13:06,734 --> 00:13:09,564
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan empatimu pada pasien...</font>

169
00:13:10,104 --> 00:13:12,875
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan menjadi obat medis terbaik...</font>

170
00:13:12,875 --> 00:13:15,204
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang bisa kau berikan
pada pasien.</font>

171
